{{Quote|[&hellip;] the Falleen nobility had been virtually wiped out by a genetic warfare experiment, one that was initiated by Lord Vader. Of that family grouping, the only surviving member was Prince Xizor, who was then the head of the Black Sun organization.|[[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett]]|<ref name="Hard Merchandise">''[[Hard Merchandise]]''</ref>}}
'''House Sizhran''' was a family of [[Falleen/Legends|Falleen]] nobles from the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of the [[Falleen (planet)/Legends|same name]]. The family included [[Haxim]] and his [[Xizor's mother|wife]], two [[Xizor's brother|sons]], including the [[Dark Prince]] [[Xizor/Legends|Xizor]], and [[Xizor's sister|two]] [[Xizor's second sister|daughters]]. 

Xizor became the [[Underlord]] of the [[Black Sun/Legends|Black Sun]] crime syndicate. Xizor was off-planet when most of his family was [[Death/Legends|killed]] when [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]] ordered Falleen [[Bombardment of Falleen|to be "sterilized"]] in [[7 BBY/Legends|7 BBY]]. The victims included three of Xizor's uncles.<ref name="The Secrets of Star Wars: Shadows of the Empire">''[[The Secrets of Star Wars: Shadows of the Empire]]''</ref>

